    <preface>
      <p><b>HOLOCAUST (RETURN OF CULTURAL OBJECTS) (AMENDMENT) ACT 2019</b></p>
      <p><span style="color:#000000">EXPLANATORY NOTES</span></p>
    </preface>
    <mainBody>
      <toc>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2019/20/notes" level="1"><inline name="tocHeading">The whole Explanatory Note</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2019/20/notes/section/1" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Overview of the Act</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2019/20/notes/section/2" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Policy background</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2019/20/notes/section/3" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Legal background</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2019/20/notes/section/4" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Territorial extent and application</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2019/20/notes/section/5" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Commentary on provisions of Act</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 1: Repeal of Sunset Provision in the Holocaust (Return of Cultural Objects) Act 2009</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 2: Extent, Commencement and Short Title</inline></tocItem>
